Package: gcsAnndataR
Type: Package
Title: Access h5ad Files on Google Cloud Storage from R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Masahiro Kanai
Maintainer: Masahiro Kanai <mkanai@broadinstitute.org>
Description: Provides R wrappers for the 'gcs_anndata' Python package, allowing R users 
    to access h5ad files stored on Google Cloud Storage without downloading the entire file.
    This package enables partial reading of AnnData objects directly from cloud storage,
    making it efficient for working with large single-cell datasets.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    Matrix,
    R6,
    reticulate
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
